THIS FACE

this face i do not see
reveals all as all to all
this face alight
with pleasure shared
perverse devine
perversion freed
perversion one
in you and me
pleasure freed
pleasure need
energy released
ceased the seed
pleasures coil unleached
tantra breath
shiva breeze
rushing through
spun entwind
vodoo rithe
shamonic rite
pagan dance
fertility birth
natures own
pulse tunned
extactic cataclysm
fruits of seed
orgamic dream
eggs fusion stired
loaded for life
a face i can not see
soon revealed
